Welcome to the Self-Assessment Hub

Your Journey of Growth Starts Here. Welcome to MOHI’s Leadership Development Self-Assessment Home. This is your space to pause, reflect, and realign as you grow in your leadership walk.

Here, you’ll discover tools that help you:

  • Check in on your well-being and find ways to stay resilient.
  • Explore your personality and uncover how your unique design shapes the way you lead and connect.
  • Reflect on your leadership journey and identify next steps forward.
  • Use guided reflection tools to nurture Christ-centered leadership.
  • Open pathways for growth with mentorship and development resources.

Created by Missions of Hope International – Leadership Development Department
